{"tid":1022101,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"請教各位前輩","createTime":"2019-02-14T17:50:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-15T04:54:05.000Z","uid":73052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"39738e010387d0d43f86b33282005e020f472b86","tid":1022101,"uid":73052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T17:50:57.000Z","msg":"出嚟做嘢都好幾年<br />\n而家搵到啲錢 就想幫父母買醫療保險<br />\n但又唔想用保險個醫療融資plan<br />\n想自己月供收息股去cover 保費<br />\n兩老年事已高 兩位加埋每年保費都要3 4萬<br />\n請教各位 個收息股要點部置好？<br />\n<br />\nP.s. 保險個醫療融資 就年供8萬 供6年 再等多4年 第十一年就夠cover一個人嘅保費<br />\n所以想自己整個收息組合 彈性啲 唔洗比人抽水 又可以當儲錢<br />\n<br />\n門外漢一名 比我做次伸手黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51ea50de0c806e95b06fdf8d04b667dbe243d9e0","tid":1022101,"uid":73052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T19:04:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4d6a5c0321fb357db60d81d1ef06d4bafb19e26","tid":1022101,"uid":73052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T04:54:05.000Z","msg":"推"}]}